dct_description_sm: This collection contains shapefiles representing key statistics from the Censos nacionales VI de población y V de vivienda 2007 of El Salvador. The original questionairre along with other supporting documentation is included with each download.
System requirements: Geographic Information Systems (GIS) software that reads ESRI shapefile format.
dct_creator_sm: El Salvador, Dirección General de Estadística y Censos
